description: Nilörngruppen AB engages in the design, manufacture, and sale of labels and label concepts. The company is headquartered in Boras, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 526 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-06-12. The firm's offering includes a range of woven-, textile-, paper-, silicone & plastic- and embossed labels; embroidered badges; packaging solutions; lanyards; metal branding products, and Retail Information System (RIS) and Radio Frequency Identification (RFID) solutions, among others. The firm operates internationally and has offices and manufacturing facilities located in Sweden, Denmark, Germany, United Kingdom, Portugal, Turkey, Hong Kong and India. Nilorngruppen AB is a subsidiary of AB Traction.
name: Nilorngruppen AB
